{"id": "1001592", "question": "matplotlib.pyplot中怎么把legend放到图片外面去？", "description": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10\"><p>比如下面的图，legend（图例）在图片里面，对图像有遮挡。</p><p>怎么设置可以把图例放在图片的外面？</p><p><img data-filename=\"p1.png\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"width: 366px;\"/><br/></p></div>", "viewer": 15620, "tags": ["统计/机器学习", "数据可视化", "Python"], "answers": [{"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>试试</p><pre><code class=\"python\">plt.legend( bbox_to_anchor=(1,1), loc='center left')</code></pre><p><br/></p></div>", "lvl2_answer": []}, {"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>我都是用</p><pre><code class=\"python\">plt.legend(loc=[1, 0])</code></pre><p><br/></p></div>", "lvl2_answer": []}]}